WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.680
Welcome to Shanghai.

00:03.680 --> 00:11.200
This big city in East China has a population of 23.5 million.

00:11.200 --> 00:15.920
It's on a wide river called the Huangpu River.

00:15.920 --> 00:20.800
The tall building you can see is the Jin Mao Tower.

00:20.800 --> 00:26.000
It's 420.5 meters high.

00:26.000 --> 00:27.680
This is Hong Kong.

00:27.920 --> 00:32.320
It's a busy city on the South China coast.

00:32.320 --> 00:35.520
Seven million people live here.

00:35.520 --> 00:38.720
The hill is Victoria Peak.

00:38.720 --> 00:42.560
It's 552 meters high.

